We were not able to define a function that takes a column name as argument and passed it to another command.
Example:
```
def size2int-col [p] {
	format filesize $p B | str from $p | str find-replace -a ',' '' $p | str to-int $p
}

def size2int [] {
	size2int-col size
}

ls | size2int
```

